description:
I`a`s Brionne travels with the Seafolk people does shows with Ia to support them as Kanoa hasn`t found any significant treasures. They heard of a storm that sunk a ship long ago near Melemele Island and they managed to find the ship but were unable to recover the cargo because a Dadarin was guarding it.
Brionne spent some time with Lana`s Popplio to help it train to get stronger so it could properly use the Z-Move Hydro Vortex. I`a`s Brionne got to tired out trying to fight off Dadarin and Lana`s Popplio training proved successful as it was able to use the move to save everyone on the boat from drowning in the whirlpool created by Dadarin.
name: Osyamari (I`a)
